text: Puerto Rico Highway 873 (PR-873) is a road located in the municipality of San Juan, Puerto Rico, and it corresponds to an original segment of the historic Carretera Central. The General Norzagaray Bridge is located on this route. With ==Major intersections== ==See also== *List of highways numbered 873 ==References== ==External links== * 873 Category:San Juan, Puerto Rico
